Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Illegal movement of animals.

Control measures
Measures applied: vaccination in response to the outbreak(s); disinfection/disinfestations; stamping out; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures

